Hi!

88
00:14:18,220 --> 00:14:19,980
<i>All right, Ed…</i>

89
00:14:20,050 --> 00:14:26,050
<i>First, enter the ISSP’s main</i>
<i>computer, and look for section 13.</i>

90
00:14:26,160 --> 00:14:28,750
Aye, aye!

91
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:33,160
