exist to the general public.

92
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:35,930
<i>It’s a pretty tall order…</i>
<i>Can you do it?</i>

93
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,030
Yup!

94
00:15:08,100 --> 00:15:09,160
Hello!

95
00:15:25,090 --> 00:15:26,550
Found it!

96
00:15:27,450 --> 00:15:31,650
<i>After you open it, find the</i>
<i>file with the code name “Tongpu.”</i>

97
00:15:31,730 --> 00:15:33,890
Yup!

98
00:16:16,800 --> 00:16:17,840
Peek-a…

99
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:20,140
…boo!

100
00:17:47,160 --> 00:17:50,960
<i>ISSP Assassination Ability,</i>
<i>Improvement Experiment.</i>

101
00:17:51,030 --> 00:17:54,090
<i>Experiment sample chart number 46.</i>

102
00:17:54,170 --> 00:17:56,230
<i>Code name: Tongpu.</i>

103
00:17:56,340 --> 00:17:59,500
<i>Confirmed a strong regression</i>
<i>of the mind during…</i>

104
00:17:59,570 --> 00:18:02,700
<i>…the experiment.</i>
<i>Experiment was canceled.</i>

105
00:18:02,780 --> 00:18:07,110
<i>Sample to be permanently kept</i>
<i>in a quarantine facility,</i>

106
00:18:31,970 --> 00:18:36,380
In the beginning, he escaped
from the facilities to seek revenge…

107
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:40,350
